title: Lanes closed after car hits motorway central reservation
text:
0 comments 
LANES are closed on a Hampshire motorway after a crash. 
Two lanes are closed eastbound on the M27 between junction 11 at Fareham and junction 12 at Port Solent after a car crashed into the central reservation. Share article 
The lanes have now reopened but delays are expected as far back as junction eight at Bursledon .
